              >Web Design</span
            ><span class="sr-only"> - </span><span
              class="mt-6 block max-w-5xl font-display text-5xl font-medium tracking-tight text-zinc-800 [text-wrap:balance] sm:text-6xl"
              >Transform your vision into a stunning website</span
            >
          </h1>
          <div class="mt-6 max-w-3xl text-xl text-zinc-600">
            <p>
              Beautiful, functional, and responsive websites designed to help
              your business succeed.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-32 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-8xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div
          class="flex flex-col gap-y-8 lg:flex-row lg:items-center lg:justify-end lg:gap-x-8 xl:gap-x-20"
        >
          <div
            class="text-xl font-light text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed space-y-6"
          >
            <h2 class="text-zinc-800 text-5xl sm:text-6xl font-medium">
              Our Approach to Design
            </h2>
            <p>
              We believe that the best websites are born out of collaboration.
              We take the time to understand your business, brand, and goals to
              craft a website that reflects your unique identity and vision
            </p>
            <ul
              role="list"
              class="mt-8 grid grid-cols-1 gap-4 text-sm leading-6 text-zinc-600 sm:grid-cols-2 sm:gap-6"
            >
              <li class="flex gap-x-3">
                <svg
                  class="h-6 w-5 flex-none text-purple-700"
                  viewBox="0 0 20 20"
                  fill="currentColor"
                  aria-hidden="true"
                >
                  <path
                    fill-rule="evenodd"
                    d="M16.704 4.153a.75.75 0 01.143 1.052l-8 10.5a.75.75 0 01-1.127.075l-4.5-4.5a.75.75 0 011.06-1.06l3.894 3.893 7.48-9.817a.75.75 0 011.05-.143z"
                    clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
                Understanding your brand and audience
              </li>
              <li class="flex gap-x-3">
                <svg
                  class="h-6 w-5 flex-none text-purple-700"
