              ></path>
            </svg>
            Sometimes, all your website needs are a few changes to feel fresh again.
            We can update specific elements like your homepage, color scheme, or
            typography to bring a modern touch while keeping your core design intact.
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-x-3">
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke-width="1.5"
              stroke="currentColor"
              class="h-6 w-5 flex-none text-purple-700"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                d="M4.5 12a7.5 7.5 0 0 0 15 0m-15 0a7.5 7.5 0 1 1 15 0m-15 0H3m16.5 0H21m-1.5 0H12m-8.457 3.077 1.41-.513m14.095-5.13 1.41-.513M5.106 17.785l1.15-.964m11.49-9.642 1.149-.964M7.501 19.795l.75-1.3m7.5-12.99.75-1.3m-6.063 16.658.26-1.477m2.605-14.772.26-1.477m0 17.726-.26-1.477M10.698 4.614l-.26-1.477M16.5 19.794l-.75-1.299M7.5 4.205 12 12m6.894 5.785-1.149-.964M6.256 7.178l-1.15-.964m15.352 8.864-1.41-.513M4.954 9.435l-1.41-.514M12.002 12l-3.75 6.495"
              ></path>
            </svg>
            Your website should evolve with your business. We offer ongoing support
            to keep your site optimized, implementing improvements over time to ensure
            it stays up-to-date, secure, and fully functional.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-32 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-8xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div
          class="flex flex-col gap-y-8 lg:flex-row lg:items-center lg:justify-end lg:gap-x-8 xl:gap-x-20"
        >
          <div
            class="text-xl font-light text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed space-y-6"
          >
            <h2 class="text-zinc-800 text-5xl sm:text-6xl font-medium">
              What makes us different
            </h2>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-zinc-700">
              Flexible and A La Carte services
            </h3>
            <p>
              We believe in flexibility and customization. Whether you're
              looking for a full website overhaul, a simple touch-up, or just a
              few key elements designed, we offer an A La Carte service model.
              This means we build what you need, when you need it, without
              forcing you into a one-size-fits-all package.
            </p>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-zinc-700">Tailored to your needs</h3>
            <p>
              We don't believe in a one-size-fits-all solution. Our process is
              entirely adaptable,choose the specific services that fit your
              goals and budget, and we'll deliver high-quality designs that meet
              your exact requirements. Whether you need a full redesign or just
              a few touch-ups, we'll create a solution that works for you.
            </p>
            <ul
              role="list"
              class="mt-8 grid grid-cols-1 gap-4 text-sm leading-6 text-zinc-600 sm:grid-cols-2 sm:gap-6"
            >
              <li class="flex gap-x-3">
                <svg
                  class="h-6 w-5 flex-none text-purple-700"
                  viewBox="0 0 20 20"
                  fill="currentColor"
                  aria-hidden="true"
                >
                  <path
                    fill-rule="evenodd"
                    d="M16.704 4.153a.75.75 0 01.143 1.052l-8 10.5a.75.75 0 01-1.127.075l-4.5-4.5a.75.75 0 011.06-1.06l3.894 3.893 7.48-9.817a.75.75 0 011.05-.143z"
                    clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
                Flexibility, from complete website design to minor updates, we cater
                to your specific needs.
              </li>
              <li class="flex gap-x-3">
                <svg
                  class="h-6 w-5 flex-none text-purple-700"
                  viewBox="0 0 20 20"
                  fill="currentColor"
                  aria-hidden="true"
                >
                  <path
                    fill-rule="evenodd"
                    d="M16.704 4.153a.75.75 0 01.143 1.052l-8 10.5a.75.75 0 01-1.127.075l-4.5-4.5a.75.75 0 011.06-1.06l3.894 3.893 7.48-9.817a.75.75 0 011.05-.143z"
                    clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
                Personalized approach, we collaborate closely with you to ensure
                your website reflects your vision and business goals.
              </li>
              <li class="flex gap-x-3">
